A Wife’s Journey Through The Multiverse | Ingress | Full 2025 Sci-Fi Movie - A woman with the ability to travel between parallel realities is shattered when she loses her husband in a tragic accident. To heal, she must confront her past trauma and journey through the multiverse in search of a reality where he’s still alive.

Watch Ingress, a full sci-fi drama and action movie about love, loss, and the power of parallel realities. After a tragic accident takes her husband, a woman with the ability to travel between multiple universes must confront her past trauma and navigate the multiverse in search of a reality where he is still alive. Perfect for fans of sci-fi thrillers, full free action movies, multiverse adventures, emotional drama films, and high-stakes science fiction stories, Ingress delivers suspense, heart, and a gripping journey across realities in the quest to reclaim love and hope.

Stars: Rachel Noll James, Johnny Ferro, Christopher Clark
